00:50:41.840 --> 00:50:44.110
My question is, when there's
a creative difference

00:50:44.110 --> 00:50:46.725
or disagreement, how
do you resolve it?

00:50:46.725 --> 00:50:48.100
BERNARD PETIOT:
First of all, you

00:50:48.100 --> 00:50:50.410
have to look at the globality.

00:50:50.410 --> 00:50:52.660
So we are inviting
these creators

00:50:52.660 --> 00:50:54.880
to come in Cirque du
Soliel, but we're also

00:50:54.880 --> 00:50:58.240
assigning what we call
a director of creation.

00:50:58.240 --> 00:51:00.640
This person is to
manage the environment

00:51:00.640 --> 00:51:02.140
and manage that dialogue.

00:51:02.140 --> 00:51:06.200
And sometimes this tension,
it's not nice every day.

00:51:06.200 --> 00:51:08.320
There's sometimes all
of these tensions.

00:51:08.320 --> 00:51:13.150
And eventually, this group will
have to come up to an agreement

00:51:13.150 --> 00:51:14.260
or take an option.

00:51:14.260 --> 00:51:17.890
Obviously, the stage
director has a lot of power

00:51:17.890 --> 00:51:21.580
because he wants to protect
the basic or the intent.

00:51:21.580 --> 00:51:25.360
On my side, I have an equipment
designer and a performance

00:51:25.360 --> 00:51:26.020
designer.

00:51:26.020 --> 00:51:30.470
And as soon as it steps
into the exposure of risk,

00:51:30.470 --> 00:51:32.950
which could be life
threatening, then that's

00:51:32.950 --> 00:51:34.620
where the buck stops.

00:51:34.620 --> 00:51:37.630
And so then it will be a no no.

00:51:37.630 --> 00:51:40.180
Everything else after that
is open for discussion,

00:51:40.180 --> 00:51:42.430
open for dialogue,
open for conversation.

00:51:45.040 --> 00:51:47.950
And obviously, as you go
up to the [NON-ENGLISH],,

00:51:47.950 --> 00:51:52.090
there will be time by which then
you realize that this is not

00:51:52.090 --> 00:51:54.730
possible, or this
could be dangerous,

00:51:54.730 --> 00:51:58.540
or this will not render what
you're looking at in terms

00:51:58.540 --> 00:52:02.132
of the expectation
of performance.

00:52:02.132 --> 00:52:04.590
BRADLEY HOROWITZ: Just in terms
